name: Warp Street LITE
description: G.R.A.S. Gaming Racing and Sims presents, Warp Street LITE. This game is an experiment for an upcoming racing game. There are no races, no AI, and nothing to worry about. Credit goes to my friend Anthony, he helped me create some of game. Including the Copperhead, some of the cheat codes, a little bit of the game art, and some of the other ideas in the game. You can find him on scratch at https://scratch.mit.edu/users/AxolotlLoops/
